# Browser Utilities

The browser package contains utility functions that are designed to work in browser environments and may use browser-specific APIs.

## Key Files

- [getImageRect.ts](mdc:packages/browser/getImageRect.ts): Utility for getting the dimensions of an image
- [getBase64Image.js](mdc:packages/browser/getBase64Image.js): Converts an image to base64 encoding
- [debounce.ts](mdc:packages/browser/debounce.ts): Function for debouncing function calls
- [shallowEqual.ts](mdc:packages/browser/shallowEqual.ts): Performs shallow equality checks on objects
- [retry.js](mdc:packages/browser/retry.js): Utility for retrying failed operations
- [Queue.js](mdc:packages/browser/Queue.js): Implementation of a queue data structure
- [isClient.ts](mdc:packages/browser/isClient.ts): Check if code is running in a browser environment

## Sub-directories

- [array/](mdc:packages/browser/array): Array manipulation utilities
- [string/](mdc:packages/browser/string): String manipulation utilities
- [regex/](mdc:packages/browser/regex): Regular expression utilities
- [sizeof/](mdc:packages/browser/sizeof): Utilities for determining memory usage
